        "TileImage": "$($repository e429d9b0-cced-4a71-a35c-b7d654a5d4e1).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to Berlin 47,\rYour next targets are Edelgard Winter and her lover. Edelgard has been cheating on her boyfriend for one year straight. When she was found out, she tried to shift the blame to her now ex-boyfriend and left with Gustav, the lover. \rThe ex has hired us to take them out both in a fit of rage. They will be partying in Der Hölle tonight. Make sure that party ends soon.\rI will leave you to prepare.",
